    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aGuideHub!  To remove shadow of mui accordion in React js, set  in . It will remove shadow of mui accordion in react js. Today, I am…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! </p>\n<p>To remove shadow of mui accordion in React js, set <code class=\"language-text\">box-shadow: none !important;</code> in <code class=\"language-text\">.MuiPaper-elevation</code>. It will remove shadow of mui accordion in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how remove shadow of mui accordion in react js.</p>\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<p>Install the following packages to use mui accordion in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npm install @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">yarn</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">yarn add @mui<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react @emotion<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>styled</code></pre></div>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install MUI and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import Material-UI accordion.</li>\n<li>Define css for the Accordion component.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Step 1: Install MUI and create a new React app.</h3>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Import Material-UI accordion.</h3>\n<p>After installing <code class=\"language-text\">MUI</code>, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following line to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Accordion<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> AccordionDetails<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> AccordionSummary<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Typography <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ExpandMoreIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/icons-material/ExpandMore'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 3: Define css for the Accordion component.</h3>\n<p>You can use the <code class=\"language-text\">accordion</code> component in your react js. For example, The accordion component is used for collapsible panels. You can use this mui class <code class=\"language-text\">.MuiPaper-elevation</code> and remove shadow of mui accordion.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.MuiPaper-elevation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none <span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>MUI material remove shadow of mui accordion example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example, to remove shadow of mui accordion, you need to import <code class=\"language-text\">accordion</code> Component. You can use <code class=\"language-text\">.MuiPaper-elevation</code> and it will remove shadow of mui accordion.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> Accordion<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> AccordionDetails<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> AccordionSummary<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Typography <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/material'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ExpandMoreIcon <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@mui/icons-material/ExpandMore'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"./App.css\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Accordion\n    <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>AccordionSummary\n        expandIcon<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ExpandMoreIcon <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        aria<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>controls<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"panel1a-content\"</span>\n        id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"panel1a-header\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Typography<span class=\"token operator\">></span>Accordion Title<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Typography<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>AccordionSummary<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>AccordionDetails<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Typography<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n        <span class=\"token constant\">A</span> <span class=\"token constant\">URL</span> slug is a part that comes at the very end <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> a <span class=\"token constant\">URL</span> and is the\n        exact address <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> a specific page on your website<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n        <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Typography<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>AccordionDetails<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Accordion<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.css</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.MuiPaper-elevation</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none <span class=\"token important\">!important</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">@mui/material</code> component and removed shadow of mui accordion in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/102980ee7a8f9384eb7ea9450c86c5d0/ec897/remove-shadow.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.556962025316455%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRkIAAABXRUJQVlA4IDYAAADwAgCdASoUAAMALplotFokKCgoCACYSzgCmAB6HnZXgAD+9jR5NRlqxaJJgCF/9ckQ2JYAAAA='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, Mui, remove, shadow\"\n        title=\"React, Mui, remove, shadow\"\n        src=\"/static/102980ee7a8f9384eb7ea9450c86c5d0/8aab1/remove-shadow.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/102980ee7a8f9